<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>台股分析站 v4</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0b0d12;--bg2:#111318;--bg3:#181b24;--bg4:#1e2130;
  --border:#1e2235;--border2:#272d42;
  --text:#e2e5f0;--text2:#848da8;--text3:#454d68;
  --up:#f04a58;--up-bg:rgba(240,74,88,0.08);--up-border:rgba(240,74,88,0.22);
  --down:#1db870;--down-bg:rgba(29,184,112,0.08);--down-border:rgba(29,184,112,0.22);
  --accent:#5b5ef4;--accent2:#7c7ff7;--gold:#f0a030;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;min-height:100vh;}
.layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:268px 1fr;min-height:100vh;}
.sidebar{background:var(--bg2);border-right:1px solid var(--border);padding:18px 13px;position:sticky;top:0;height:100vh;overflow-y:auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;}
.main{padding:22px;overflow-x:hidden;}
.sidebar-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:6px 4px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:10px;}
.logo-icon{width:34px;height:34px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#5b5ef4,#7c7ff7);border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(91,94,244,.3);}
.logo-text{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;}
.logo-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;}
.search-box{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:10px;padding:8px 10px;display:flex;gap:7px;margin-bottom:4px;transition:border-color .15s;}
.search-box:focus-within{border-color:var(--accent);}
.search-box input{flex:1;background:none;border:none;color:var(--text);font-size:14px;font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;outline:none;min-width:0;}
.search-box input::placeholder{color:var(--text3);}
.search-box button{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:7px;padding:5px 12px;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-weight:500;}
.search-box button:hover{opacity:.85;}
.sidebar-label{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:8px 4px 4px;}
.stock-btn{background:none;border:none;border-radius:9px;padding:8px 10px;cursor:pointer;text-align:left;width:100%;color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;transition:all .15s;}
.stock-btn:hover{background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text);}
.stock-btn.active{background:rgba(91,94,244,.14);color:var(--accent2);}
.stock-btn-code{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);}
.stock-btn.active .stock-btn-code{color:var(--accent2);opacity:.7;}
.section{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.section-title{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:15px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.section-title::before{content:'';width:3px;height:13px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:2px;display:inline-block;}
.stock-hero{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:20px;align-items:start;}
.hero-name{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px;}
.hero-code{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;}
.hero-price{font-size:42px;font-weight:700;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;line-height:1;text-align:right;}
.hero-change{font-size:14px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:8px;display:inline-block;margin-top:7px;}
.up-c{color:var(--up);}.dn-c{color:var(--down);}
.up-tag{background:var(--up-bg);border:1px solid var(--up-border);color:var(--up);}
.dn-tag{background:var(--down-bg);border:1px solid var(--down-border);color:var(--down);}
.metrics-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:9px;margin-top:14px;}
.metric-card{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:11px;padding:11px 13px;}
.mc-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:4px;}
.mc-value{font-size:17px;font-weight:600;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;}
.range-wrap{margin-top:14px;}
.range-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:6px;}
.range-track{height:5px;background:var(--border2);border-radius:3px;position:relative;}
.range-grad{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--down),#f0a030,var(--up));border-radius:3px;}
.range-dot{width:12px;height:12px;background:#fff;border:2px solid var(--accent);border-radius:50%;position:absolute;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);}
.kline-controls{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:11px;}
.kline-verdict-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px;}
.period-group{display:flex;gap:4px;}
.pbtn{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text3);font-size:12px;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:6px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;}
.pbtn.active{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);color:#fff;}
.kline-canvas-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;}
#klineCanvas{width:100%;display:block;border-radius:8px 8px 0 0;}
#volCanvas{width:100%;display:block;border-radius:0 0 8px 8px;}
.kline-vol-divider{height:1px;background:var(--border);}
.kline-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;color:var(--text3);background:var(--bg2);border-radius:10px;}
.badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:5px;white-space:nowrap;}
.b-bull{background:rgba(240,74,88,.12);color:#f87171;border:1px solid rgba(240,74,88,.25);}
.b-bear{background:rgba(29,184,112,.12);color:#4ade80;border:1px solid rgba(29,184,112,.25);}
.b-neu{background:rgba(91,94,244,.1);color:var(--accent2);border:1px solid rgba(91,94,244,.2);}
.b-load{background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text3);border:1px solid var(--border2);}
.b-amber{background:rgba(245,158,11,.1);color:#fbbf24;border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.25);}
.news-item{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:13px 15px;margin-bottom:8px;text-decoration:none;display:block;transition:all .15s;}
.news-item:hover{border-color:var(--accent);}
.ni-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:7px;}
.ni-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.ni-src{font-size:10px;color:var(--accent2);background:rgba(91,94,244,.1);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;}
.ni-time{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;}
.ni-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.7;margin-top:6px;}
.related-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:9px;}
.related-card{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:13px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;}
.related-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent);}
.rc-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:2px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
.rc-code{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:9px;}
.rc-price{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:3px;}
.rc-change{font-size:11px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;}
.verdict-box{border-radius:14px;padding:18px 20px;margin-bottom:14px;}
.verdict-bull{background:rgba(240,74,88,.06);border:1px solid rgba(240,74,88,.2);}
.verdict-bear{background:rgba(29,184,112,.06);border:1px solid rgba(29,184,112,.2);}
.verdict-neu{background:rgba(245,158,11,.06);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.2);}
.verdict-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:13px;}
.verdict-icon{font-size:30px;}
.verdict-label{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;}
.verdict-sublabel{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:2px;}
.verdict-score-row{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:12px;}
.score-pill{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:20px;padding:5px 13px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);}
.score-pill strong{color:var(--text);}
.verdict-entry{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 15px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.entry-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:5px;}
.entry-value{font-size:21px;font-weight:700;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;}
.entry-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:3px;line-height:1.6;}
.entry-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;}
.verdict-reason{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.75;padding:11px 14px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);}
.verdict-disclaimer{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:8px;line-height:1.5;}
.loading-box{text-align:center;padding:3.5rem 1rem;color:var(--text3);}
.spinner{width:28px;height:28px;border:2px solid var(--border2);border-top-color:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;animation:spin .8s linear infinite;margin:0 auto 12px;}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg);}}
.error-box{background:rgba(240,74,88,.07);border:1px solid rgba(240,74,88,.2);border-radius:12px;padding:15px;color:#f87171;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;}
.empty-box{text-align:center;padding:2.5rem;color:var(--text3);font-size:13px;}
.welcome{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:65vh;text-align:center;gap:13px;color:var(--text3);}
.welcome-icon{font-size:52px;margin-bottom:5px;}
.welcome h2{font-size:20px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text2);}
.welcome p{font-size:14px;max-width:380px;line-height:1.75;}
.welcome-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:8px;margin-top:4px;}
.welcome-chip{background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:20px;padding:5px 13px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;}
.welcome-chip:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent2);}
.inner-tabs{display:flex;gap:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:15px;overflow-x:auto;}
.itab{padding:7px 15px;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:none;color:var(--text3);border-bottom:2px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-1px;transition:all .15s;font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;white-space:nowrap;}
.itab.active{color:var(--accent2);border-bottom-color:var(--accent);}
.itab:hover:not(.active){color:var(--text2);}
.ipanel{display:none;}
.ipanel.active{display:block;}
.sidebar-tabs{display:flex;gap:0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:8px;}
.stab{flex:1;padding:6px 0;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:none;color:var(--text3);border-bottom:2px solid transparent;margin-bottom:-1px;transition:all .15s;font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;text-align:center;}
.stab.active{color:var(--accent2);border-bottom-color:var(--accent);}
.spanel{display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;}
.spanel.active{display:flex;}
.lu-row{display:flex;align-items:center;padding:6px 7px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:background .12s;}
.lu-row:hover{background:var(--bg3);}
.lu-rank{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;width:18px;flex-shrink:0;}
.lu-name{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);flex:1;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;}
.lu-code{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;margin-right:5px;}
.lu-pct{font-size:11px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;color:var(--up);background:var(--up-bg);border:1px solid var(--up-border);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:4px;flex-shrink:0;}
.sector-tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:11px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:5px;background:rgba(91,94,244,.1);color:var(--accent2);border:1px solid rgba(91,94,244,.2);margin-top:4px;}
.industry-tag{display:inline-flex;font-size:10px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text3);border:1px solid var(--border2);margin-left:6px;}
#klineTooltip{position:absolute;pointer-events:none;display:none;background:#1a1d2a;border:1px solid #2e3548;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 13px;font-size:12px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;color:#e2e5f0;line-height:1.8;z-index:50;min-width:145px;box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.5);}
@media(max-width:820px){
  .layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .sidebar{position:relative;height:auto;}
  .metrics-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  .stock-hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .hero-price{text-align:left;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="layout">
<aside class="sidebar">
  <div class="sidebar-logo">
    <div class="logo-icon">📈</div>
    <div>
      <div class="logo-text">台股分析站 <span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);">v4</span></div>
      <div class="logo-sub">Yahoo Finance · 延遲15分鐘</div>
      <div id="marketBadge" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;font-size:10px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;margin-top:2px;background:rgba(70,80,104,.15);color:var(--text3);border:1px solid var(--border2);">⚫ 盤前</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="search-box">
    <input type="text" id="stockInput" placeholder="輸入代號，例：2330">
    <button onclick="searchStock()">查詢</button>
  </div>
  <div class="sidebar-tabs" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);">
    <button class="stab active" onclick="switchSideTab('hot')">熱門</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="switchSideTab('limitup')">漲停🔥</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="switchSideTab('lowbase')">低基</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="switchSideTab('trend')">趨勢</button>
    <button class="stab" onclick="switchSideTab('winrate')">勝率🏆</button>
  </div>
  <div class="spanel active" id="spanel-hot">
    <div class="sidebar-label">半導體/AI</div>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('2330')"><span>台積電</span><span class="stock-btn-code">2330</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('2303')"><span>聯電</span><span class="stock-btn-code">2303</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('2454')"><span>聯發科</span><span class="stock-btn-code">2454</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('2382')"><span>廣達</span><span class="stock-btn-code">2382</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('6669')"><span>緯穎</span><span class="stock-btn-code">6669</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('3017')"><span>奇鋐</span><span class="stock-btn-code">3017</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('3711')"><span>日月光</span><span class="stock-btn-code">3711</span></button>
    <div class="sidebar-label">傳產/金融/ETF</div>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('2317')"><span>鴻海</span><span class="stock-btn-code">2317</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('2412')"><span>中華電</span><span class="stock-btn-code">2412</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('2002')"><span>中鋼</span><span class="stock-btn-code">2002</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('2891')"><span>中信金</span><span class="stock-btn-code">2891</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('0050')"><span>元大台灣50</span><span class="stock-btn-code">0050</span></button>
    <button class="stock-btn" onclick="quickSearch('00878')"><span>國泰永續高息</span><span class="stock-btn-code">00878</span></button>
  </div>
  <div class="spanel" id="spanel-limitup"><div id="limitUpList" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;padding:20px 0;">點擊「漲停 🔥」載入</div></div>
  <div class="spanel" id="spanel-lowbase"><div id="lowBaseList" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;padding:20px 0;">點擊「低基期」載入</div></div>
  <div class="spanel" id="spanel-trend"><div id="trendList" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;padding:20px 0;">點擊「趨勢」載入</div></div>
  <div class="spanel" id="spanel-winrate"><div id="winrateList" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;padding:20px 0;">點擊「勝率🏆」載入</div></div>
</aside>

<main class="main" id="mainArea">
  <div class="welcome" id="welcomeState">
    <div class="welcome-icon">📊</div>
    <h2>台股個股分析站 v4</h2>
    <p>從左側選擇股票，或輸入代號查詢。<br>✅ 無需 Allow CORS 擴充套件</p>
    <div class="welcome-chips">
      <div class="welcome-chip" onclick="quickSearch('2330')">台積電 2330</div>
      <div class="welcome-chip" onclick="quickSearch('2454')">聯發科 2454</div>
      <div class="welcome-chip" onclick="quickSearch('2382')">廣達 2382</div>
      <div class="welcome-chip" onclick="quickSearch('0050')">元大台灣50</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
</div>

<script>
// ─── 所有 API 都透過 Vercel proxy，不需要 Allow CORS 擴充 ───
const P = url => `/api/proxy?url=${encodeURIComponent(url)}`;

