]}</span>`:''}</div></div><span class="lu-pct">+${s.pct.toFixed(2)}%</span></div>`;}).join('')}<div style="font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);text-align:center;padding:7px 0 2px;">更新 ${now}　·　來源：證交所</div></div>`;}

